content: Software Engineer with 1.5 years of experience building frontend and backend (full-stack) web applications using TypeScript, modern frameworks, and cloud platforms including CloudFlare and Digital Ocean. Strong background in API design, authentication and authorization, database schema, and secure cloud-based systems. Experienced in working with production systems, security considerations, and scalable architectures. Adaptive learner who leverages AI tools alongside organic engineering practices to improve productivity and deliver reliable solutions.
